channel.title: TeletoX, TeleToY, TeleHight?
channel.description:
Hi,
I was wondering if there is a way to teleport to XCoords, YCoords and also Hight?
Anyone got any good coords for a underground cave which is only accesable by teleporting (you cant walk there)
Also i have made a command ::noobtrain which should teleport you to Evil Bob's island (X: 2525, Y: 4776) but it tele's to X: 3465 Y: 4776! I Have checked the code and its correct!? WTF is goin on there!!!
- toonshorty
